<taxonomicName authorityName="Alves-Silva, R. M. Silveira &amp; Drechsler-Santos" authorityYear="2020" box="[327,558,979,1003]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Hymenochaetaceae" genus="Fomitiporia" kingdom="Fungi" order="Hymenochaetales" pageId="7" pageNumber="330" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="murrillii">
<emphasis box="[327,558,979,1003]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="330">Fomitiporia murrillii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is reported in 
<collectingCountry name="Brazil" pageId="7" pageNumber="330">Brazil</collectingCountry>
</emphasis>
only from the states of 
<collectingRegion box="[447,521,1013,1037]" country="Brazil" name="Parana" pageId="7" pageNumber="330">Paraná</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[572,774,1013,1037]" country="Brazil" name="Rio Grande do Sul" pageId="7" pageNumber="330">Rio Grande do Sul</collectingRegion>
. There are no records from the Amazon region, and our record is the first from this region.
